

= "Clickworker" is a term used to describe online freelance workers. The term is usually used in reference to a worker who performs duties within a crowdsourcing platform, generally on a per-task pay rate. [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clickworkers]

Used in the plural as [[Clickworkers]], it's also the name of a specific NASA project for crowdsoursing science.



